SUMMARY:Closure: HANWELL STATION: Monday 29\, Tuesday 30 June and Wednesday
  1 July\, the station will close at 2254 each evening. Last trains will 
 call at 2233 (from Heathrow Terminal 4 to Abbey Wood) and 2252 (from Abbey
  Wood to Heathrow Terminal 5). Please use local London Buses services.
